{
  "stem": "11174.4",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 107.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And 6 o'clock was a curfew.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "If you're caught, you could be shot, especially a Jew-- only for the Jews.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "I ran to be able to beat-- I think it was about 6.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "I didn't know for sure, you know-- By the way, that watch didn't run, because the-- the handles were broken, so I couldn't-- I ran, ran, ran and I caught that guy, that farmer.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And I went up and we go back.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I say, they didn't shoot me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They realized that I was telling the truth.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I didn't know what to tell him.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Sure enough, as soon as we ride and we come before that-- before-- almost before that water at the pass, quite a bit before, maybe a kilometer or so, he says where my stuff?",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Where's my money?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He doesn't want to go with me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He doesn't want to take me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I have to pay him the money.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You promised me this, you-- they promised that one.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE] I tell him, look, I just got out with my life.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Nothing doing.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Go back to the Germans.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I'm not going to take you.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I kept on sort of a little bit struggling.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He wants me to get off.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I got off, I grabbed the wagon again.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I says I'll pay you.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They'll pay you.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know the-- he didn't want to hear, was angry.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He-- in his fantasy, he got rich already and we were all of a sudden nothing.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I said, here's the watch.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I still had-- the ring I still had.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Somehow the ring-- He took it and then I don't know how I got it back.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I don't remember him giving it to me.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
